Package hospital

package hospital
This package contains the classes that represent the hospital and its components. It contains the classes that represent the rooms, the individuals, the registry and the hospital map. It also contains the classes that represent the menus and the tools used to interact with the user. The classes in this package are used to manage the hospital and its components.
